Qualifications: FLAG-tagged Cdh1 was affinity purified and associated proteins were identified by mass spectrometry. Scoring type was unclear, but higher values indicate higher confidence in the interaction. High confidence scores for FLAG-CDH1-transfected cells with no competing peptide (2) are reported here. Negative control scores were those for non-transfected cells (0), non-transfected cells with competing FLAG peptide (0) and FLAG-CDH1-transfected cells with competing FLAG peptide (0).
